message: "If you use Authensor in your research, please cite it as below."
type: software
title: "Authensor: An Open-Source Safety Stack for AI Agents"
authors:
  - family-names: Kearney
    given-names: John
version: 1.5.0-alpha
date-released: 2025-01-01
license: MIT
url: https://authensor.com
repository-code: https://github.com/authensor/authensor
keywords:
  - ai-safety
  - agent-authorization
  - guardrails
  - content-safety
  - audit-trail
