abstract: >-
  Authensor is an open-source platform for AI agent safety providing
  action authorization via a declarative policy engine, content safety
  scanning (PII, prompt injection, credentials, exfiltration),
  tamper-evident hash-chained audit trails, human-in-the-loop approval
  workflows, and real-time anomaly detection. Covers OWASP Agentic
  Top 10, EU AI Act Articles 12/14/15, and NIST AI RMF.
